NOTE ON DATA AND SAFETY USE

All plant data, sensor values, personnel names and event timelines in this
repository are synthetic and generated by the simulation engine contained
herein. The incident scenario is a fictional composite informed by publicly
reported investigations and public regulatory standards. No real plant data is
used.

This software is a research prototype. It is not certified as a safety
instrumented system and must not be relied upon as one. Any deployment in a
live industrial environment must retain all existing independent safety
functions and comply with the applicable statutory regime.
